'''Adele McAllister''' is a Washington D.C.-based singer-songwriter. In 2014 she released a [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]]-inspired folk music album entitled ''[[Roads Go Ever On and On: Songs from Tolkien's Middle-earth]]''.
